subproject.description: The project is designed to preserve the basic health and medical services to women and children in Gaza through Renovation and Rehabilitation Works for Maternities within existing six hospitals and three PHCC’s in the Gaza Strip in order to provide enough healthy well designed maternity service spaces within the selected facilities. Number of PHCC’s maternity centres will be renovated and rehabilitated and some areas will be expanded in the Gaza Strip with a total grant value of USD 800,000 from Saudi Fund for Development
